name: αrεš
description:
αrεš is based on Uranus, one of the furthest planets in our solar system. it's composed of a rocky core surrounded by a watery surface, and a thin ring to top it all off, which is represented in this slow-moving loop.

this is part of my 𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐯𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 collection. it combines my love for space & astronomy, with an abstract monochrome art style. every artwork is a satisfying infinite loop of motion.
